Ranger Help for: flame arrow
=============================

SYNTAX:      flame arrow
             flame bolt
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to set an arrow or bolt on fire, adding fire
damage to the next shot. The Ranger needs ammo and a lit torch in their
inventory. Flaming ammo must be used quickly before it burns out.
